1. *Ustvari*, to je bio najbolji izbor. (Actually, it was the best choice.) 
2. To nije izgledalo kao da će biti tako, ali *ustvari* bilo je. (It didn't look like it would be like that, but actually it was.)
3. Ja sam mislio da će biti drugačije, ali *ustvari*, bilo je isto. (I thought it would be different, but actually, it was the same.) 
4. *Ustvario* sam da treba da se to dogodi. (I realized that it should happen.) 
5. Ona je *ustvarena* da će biti problem. (She realized that there would be a problem.)